shall]] || 8–15, 15–8, 15–7, 15–9 |- | 1993 || {{flagicon|PAK}} '''[[Jansher Khan]]''' || {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Chris Dittmar]] || 15–10, 10–15, 15–13, 15–8 |}
